Here is SQL queries with common table expression for rental duration of films:

Maximum rental duration:

	SELECT MAX (rental_duration)					
	fROM film					
  
Count of the films which have maximum rental duration:	

	SELECT COUNT (film_id)					
	FROM film					
	WHERE rental_duration = 7	
  
Minimum rental duration:

	SELECT MIN (rental_duration)					
	FROM film			
  
Count of the films which have minimum rental duration:

	SELECT COUNT (film_id)					
	FROM film					
	WHERE rental_duration = 3	
  
Average rental duration:	

	SELECT AVG(rental_duration)						
	FROM film								
